@startuml 1E_Platform_Landing_Discovery_Access
title 1-E · Platform Landing Discovery & Returning Access (UC-L01 to UC-L04, UC-L10, UC-L11)

start
|Visitor (Prospective Tenant)|
:Open Platform Landing Page;

|System|
:Render public marketing page;
:Load active feature highlights,\npricing plans and demo/screenshots;

|Visitor (Prospective Tenant)|
if (Visitor action?) then (Browse Features)
  :Browse feature sections;
  |System|
  :Display SaaS capabilities and module list;
elseif (Visitor action?) then (View Pricing)
  :Open pricing page;
  |System|
  :Fetch active public plans;
  if (Plans available?) then (No)
    :Display contact form or maintenance message;
  else (Yes)
    :Render plan comparison and CTA;
  endif
elseif (Visitor action?) then (View Demo)
  :Open demo or screenshots page;
  |System|
  :Render demo assets and screenshots;
else (Register)
  :Proceed to Tenant Registration;
endif

|Returning Tenant Admin|
if (Returning action?) then (Login)
  :Click Login to Tenant Admin;
  |System|
  :Redirect to tenant admin login;
elseif (Returning action?) then (Reset Password)
  :Enter email for password reset;
  |System|
  :Validate tenant admin email;
  if (Email exists?) then (Yes)
    :Create password reset token;
    :Send reset email;
    |Returning Tenant Admin|
    :Open reset link and submit new password;
    |System|
    :Validate token and update password hash;
  else (No)
    :Return generic reset response;
  endif
endif

stop
@enduml
